  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "1.The proportion of the disadvantaged groups especially women and Dalits in decision making positions in local institutions collaborating with different HELVETAS initiatives is increased.\r\n2.All local government institutions collaborating with different HELVETAS initiatives provide publicly available information through different means.\r\n\r\n3.Local governments in the working areas implement the annual plan activities based on periodic plan priorities and allocate budget accordingly.\r\n4.Local institutions collaborating with different HELVETAS initiatives are perceived by the primary stakeholders to provide effective, transparent and responsive services."
    },
